    <item>
      <title>约翰逊议长无视强硬派，推进乌克兰和以色列计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/speaker-johnson-defies-hardliners-presses-ahead-on-ukraine-plan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[面对共和党强硬派驱逐他的威胁，美国众议院议长迈克·约翰逊正在继续向乌克兰和以色列提供新的援助，并通知议员他将很快分发该计划的细节。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/speaker-johnson-defies-hardliners-presses-ahead-on-ukraine-plan</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 15:39:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴西国家石油公司主席重返董事会，但因竞争对手不同</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/petrobras-chair-returns-to-divided-board-of-oil-producer-in-political-showdown</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着政府任命的董事会成员与代表拉丁美洲最大石油生产商少数股东的成员之间的争执加剧，一名巴西法官恢复了巴西国家石油公司董事长的职务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/petrobras-chair-returns-to-divided-board-of-oil-producer-in-political-showdown</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 15:31:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管美国抱怨，加拿大仍将于 2024 年开始对科技巨头征税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/canada-to-start-taxing-tech-giants-in-2024-despite-us-complaints</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大将于今年开始对全球最大的科技公司征收拟议的税收，尽管美国立法者威胁要对主要针对美国公司的征税进行贸易报复。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/canada-to-start-taxing-tech-giants-in-2024-despite-us-complaints</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 15:28:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国将军警告乌克兰局势“严峻”，援助被推迟</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/us-general-warns-of-ukraine-s-dire-situation-as-aid-is-delayed</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国高级军官周三警告说，随着美国军事援助的拖延，乌克兰面临着“严峻”的战场条件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/us-general-warns-of-ukraine-s-dire-situation-as-aid-is-delayed</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 15:24:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列遇袭后七国集团考虑对伊朗实施新的空中制裁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/g-7-nations-weigh-new-iran-air-sanctions-after-attack-on-israel</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士称，一些七国集团国家正在考虑对伊朗航空实施新制裁，以回应德黑兰 4 月 13 日对以色列的袭击，此举将进一步限制伊朗航空公司飞往欧洲的航班。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/g-7-nations-weigh-new-iran-air-sanctions-after-attack-on-israel</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 15:11:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>波音公司重置安全文化还有“很长的路要走”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/boeing-has-long-way-to-go-to-fix-safety-culture-after-accident</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国立法者要求波音公司花费必要的时间和精力来重塑其安全文化，并批评该飞机制造商与监管机构的关系过于亲密。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/boeing-has-long-way-to-go-to-fix-safety-culture-after-accident</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 14:55:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>除非马杜罗迅速采取行动，否则美国将重新实施委内瑞拉石油禁令</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/us-to-reimpose-venezuela-oil-ban-unless-maduro-acts-quickly</link>
      <description><![CDATA[如果尼古拉斯·马杜罗政权在未来两天内不采取措施履行一项协议，允许在定于 7 月举行的选举中进行更公平的投票，总统乔·拜登政府打算重新对委内瑞拉实施石油制裁，结束六个月的缓刑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/us-to-reimpose-venezuela-oil-ban-unless-maduro-acts-quickly</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 14:03:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>委内瑞拉将把被扣押的康菲石油公司资产交给鲜为人知的公司</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/venezuela-to-hand-seized-conoco-oil-assets-to-little-known-firm</link>
      <description><![CDATA[委内瑞拉计划利用一家鲜为人知的公司来接管曾经由康菲石油公司运营的关键油田和设施，并在美国决定是否恢复制裁的最后期限之前迅速签署协议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/venezuela-to-hand-seized-conoco-oil-assets-to-little-known-firm</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 13:48:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列称真主党袭击加利利 14 名士兵受伤</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/hezbollah-rocket-assault-wounds-six-people-as-fight-with-israel-intensifies</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗支持的武装组织真主党用无人机和反坦克导弹袭击了以色列北部的一个村庄，造成 14 名士兵受伤。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/hezbollah-rocket-assault-wounds-six-people-as-fight-with-israel-intensifies</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 12:19:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>参议员卡丁表示，国会领导人正在讨论伊朗石油制裁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/congressional-leaders-discussing-iran-oil-sanctions-cardin-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[参议员本·卡丁周二表示，国会领导人正在讨论如何推进对伊朗石油进口商实施制裁的立法，在伊朗直接攻击以色列后，这一问题愈演愈烈。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/congressional-leaders-discussing-iran-oil-sanctions-cardin-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 22:06:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
